 are other casters (Palazious) who receive the bad end of an ass kickin' from an enraged mob. <br><br>The specifics may change from mob to mob, and from situation to situation, but it seems the short answer in general to deal with it has been suggested: if you are in front, turn off auto attack to minimize the damage and be  behind it if at all possible. Just because a mob is rampaging doesn't mean it can't still kick your butt. It just doesn't need any extra help from you <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><table border=0><tr><td><img src='http://etherealms.com/whyt/WhytsSpearSm.gif' border=0></td><td align=center valign=middle><h3>Whytspirit of the Nexus</h3>Wife to Hallace Nexusmaximus<br>( not Wubwub :p )<br>Mystic of Dark Brigade<br><br> "It's not about the loot...It's about the challenge!"<br><br><a href='http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=190375' >My Goodies </a> </td></tr></table></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub54.ezboard.com/uacturian.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Acturian</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Froglok Dar Knight</span><br>  Posts: 60<br> <font color=#00CCFF>(5/26/02 6:35:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub54.ezboard.com/fquelliousquaterstherebirthfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=649.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Would you talk to me bout rampage?</span><hr size=1> Rampage hits you anywhere, I could be on the rampage list for Vindi, and be in tormax arch (never will happen) and he'll hit me.<br><br>Enrage is riposite of all attacks to the front.<br><br>Now If I rember correctly, rampage is the top FOUR targets on a mob's hate list. I have jolted off of Zlandicar's and Vindicator's Rampage list, doomshade and 